      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个零售收银系统的状态流转图。核心场景是：从收银台发起请求，中间经过加载状态，最后可能成功或失败。如果失败，用户可以选择重试，或者彻底放弃并跳转到优惠券系统去处理异常。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_PointOfSale",
        "Idle",
        "Loading",
        "Success",
        "Error",
        "Retail_CouponSystem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。起点是Retail_PointOfSale，然后进入Idle状态。我想确认一下：Loading之后的分支，Success和Error是互斥的吗？还有Error到Idle的重试，和Error到Retail_CouponSystem的放弃，这两个动作是用户可选的对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Loading",
        "Success",
        "Error",
        "Idle",
        "Retail_CouponSystem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，Success和Error是互斥的。Loading收到数据就进Success，请求失败就进Error。Error状态给用户两个选择：Retry回到Idle重新来，或者Abort直接退出到Retail_CouponSystem。另外Success之后应该有个Reset能回到Idle。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Loading",
        "Success",
        "Error",
        "Idle",
        "Retail_CouponSystem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主框架画出来。起点Retail_PointOfSale指向Idle，Idle通过Start Request进入Loading。Loading分出两条线：Data Received到Success，Request Failed到Error。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_PointOfSale",
        "Idle",
        "Loading",
        "Success",
        "Error"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "等等，Error到Retail_CouponSystem的流转，我觉得标注成Abort更准确，表示用户主动放弃当前流程。Retry那个保持原意就行。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Error",
        "Retail_CouponSystem",
        "Idle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整。现在Error状态有两个出口：Retry回到Idle，Abort跳转到Retail_CouponSystem。Success这边我加了Reset返回Idle。整个图用stateDiagram-v2来画，结构更清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Error",
        "Idle",
        "Retail_CouponSystem",
        "Success"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "我再看一眼——Idle到Loading的触发条件是Start Request，这个没问题。不过Success和Error都是中间状态，最终都能回到Idle或者被导向外部系统，这个闭环是对的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Loading",
        "Success",
        "Error"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认无误。最终状态图包含：Retail_PointOfSale作为起点，Idle为初始状态，Loading处理请求，Success和Error分别处理正常和异常结果，Error支持Retry或Abort，Abort导向Retail_CouponSystem，Success支持Reset。所有流转条件都已标注清楚。",
